            </p>
          </section>

          <!-- Service Description -->
          <section class="terms-section">
            <h2>3. Service Description</h2>
            <h3>Application Features</h3>
            <p>
              Tatikati provides access to a curated library of children's podcasts and audio content, including:
            </p>
            <ul>
              <li>Age-appropriate podcast content for children</li>
              <li>Child-safe mode with audio navigation</li>
              <li>Carefully curated content without intrusive algorithms</li>
              <li>Offline listening capabilities</li>
              <li>Parental controls and content filtering</li>
            </ul>

