            <p>
              You may terminate your account at any time. We reserve the right to suspend or terminate your account if you violate these Terms or engage in activities that harm our service or other users.
            </p>
          </section>

          <!-- Acceptable Use -->
          <section class="terms-section">
            <h2>5. Acceptable Use</h2>
            <h3>Permitted Uses</h3>
            <p>
              You may use Tatikati for personal, non-commercial purposes in accordance with these Terms. Our content is designed for family use and children's entertainment and education.
            </p>

            <h3>Prohibited Activities</h3>
            <p>
              You agree not to:
            </p>
            <ul>
              <li>Use the service for any unlawful purpose or in violation of these Terms</li>
              <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to our systems or other users' accounts</li>
              <li>Distribute malware, viruses, or any harmful code</li>
              <li>Interfere with or disrupt the service or servers</li>
              <li>Reverse engineer, decompile, or disassemble the application</li>
              <li>Copy, reproduce, or distribute our content without authorization</li>
              <li>Use automated systems to access the service without permission</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

